judge%20ruled%20on%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoogle%20is%20a%20monopolist%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20US%20District%20Judge%20Amit%20P.%20Mehta%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.lbr.cloud%2Fpublic%2F2024-08%2F045110819896.pdf%3FVersionId%3DmHMw8uSvPbFCwl.7.yAY8wRXM0.UCmrD%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20it%20has%20acted%20as%20one%20to%20maintain%20its%20monopoly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Justice's%20case%20centered%20on%20Google's%20payments%20to%20other%20companies%2C%20like%20Apple%20and%20Samsung%2C%20to%20give%20its%20search%20engine%20prominence%20on%20their%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Google%2C%20there's%20apparently%20a%20very%20good%20reason%20to%20keep%20these%20payments%20coming%2C%20as%20the%20search%20revenue%20generated%20is%20worth%20billions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Monday's%20filing%2C%20the%20company%20estimated%20in%202017%20that%20its%20default%20placements%20across%20Safari%2C%20Firefox%2C%20and%20other%20browsers%20drove%2054%25%20of%20its%20search%20revenue.%20That%20number%20has%20only%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%2C%20Google%20has%20a%20major%20deal%20with%20Apple%20to%20keep%20Google%20the%20default%20search%20engine%20on%20Safari%2C%20which%20runs%20on%20iPhones%2C%20iPads%2C%20and%20Mac%20computers%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Google%20projected%20that%20it%20would%20lose%20between%2060%25%20and%2080%25%20of%20its%20search%20volume%20on%20Apple%20devices%20if%20it%20were%20replaced%20as%20the%20default%20general%20search%20engine%2C%20the%20filing%20said.%20That%20accounts%20for%20between%20%2428.2%20billion%20and%20%2432.7%20billion%20in%20net%20revenue%20losses%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoogle's%20distribution%20agreements%20are%20exclusive%20and%20have%20anticompetitive%20effects%2C%26quot%3B%20Mehta%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEddy%20Cue%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20services%20at%20Apple%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-apple-iphone-search-engine-safari-deal-20-billion-2022-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevealed%20in%20court%20documents%20earlier%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Google%20paid%20%2420%20billion%20in%202022%20to%20secure%20this%20spot%2C%20which%20amounted%20to%2017.5%25%20of%20Apple's%20operating%20income.%20So%2C%20any%20remedy%20that%20stops%20or%20reduces%20Google's%20search%20payments%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-google-iphone-search-deal-antitrust-ruling-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewould%20be%20bad%20news%20for%20Apple%2C%20too%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20landmark%20decision%20on%20Monday%20marked%20the%20near-conclusion%20of%20the%20DOJ's%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20search%20company%2C%20which%20was%20filed%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20happens%20next%20is%20still%20unknown%2C%20as%20the%20ruling%20did%20not%20include%20remedies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20president%20of%20global%20affairs%2C%20Kent%20Walker%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20appeal%3B%20this%20could%20be%20drawn%20out%20for%20a%20while%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20will%20undoubtedly%20have%20Google%20leaders%20concerned%2C%20particularly%20if%20remedies%20include%20forcing%20it%20to%20break%20up%20with%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-lawsuit-antitrust-case-doj-search-agreements-apple-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESome%20experts%20previously%20floated%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20worst-case%20scenario%20for%20Google%20where%20it's%20barred%20from%20bidding%20for%20the%20default%20position%20on%20devices%20while%20competitors%20still%20can%2C%20although%20this%20may%20be%20an%20extreme%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20anything%20that%20pushes%20Google%20out%20of%20that%20default%20s