%20dark-colored%20glass%20building%20at%20Google's%20headquarters%20in%20Mountain%20View%2C%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6631b3740dfb1341e901052d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20HQ%20in%20Mountain%20View%2C%20California.%3Cp%3ETayfun%20Coskun%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20was%20just%20dealt%20a%20massive%20loss%20in%20its%20landmark%20antitrust%20case.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BGoogle%20is%20a%20monopolist%2C%20and%20it%20has%20acted%20as%20one%20to%20maintain%20its%20monopoly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20wrote.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20was%20accused%20of%20spending%20billions%20to%20be%20the%20default%20search%20engine%20on%20Apple%20devices%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20violated%20antitrust%20law%20with%20its%20online%20search%2C%20a%20federal%20judge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.lbr.cloud%2Fpublic%2F2024-08%2F045110819896.pdf%3FVersionId%3DmHMw8uSvPbFCwl.7.yAY8wRXM0.UCmrD%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eruled%3C%2Fa%3E%20Monday%2C%20striking%20a%20major%20blow%20against%20one%20of%20the%20titans%20of%20the%20tech%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Judge%20Amit%20Mehta%20said%20Google's%20billions%20in%20payments%20to%20keep%20its%20search%20engine%20as%20the%20default%20on%20web%20browsers%20violated%20US%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20having%20carefully%20considered%20and%20weighed%20the%20witness%20testimony%20and%20evidence%2C%20the%20court%20reaches%20the%20following%20conclusion%3A%20Google%20is%20a%20monopolist%2C%20and%20it%20has%20acted%20as%20one%20to%20maintain%20its%20monopoly%2C%26quot%3B%20Mehta%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge's%20ruling%20follows%20a%20landmark%20antitrust%20trial%20that%20concluded%20in%20DC%20in%20May.%20The%20case%20had%20been%20closely%20watched%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20whether%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-antitrust-trial-big-tech-future-analysis-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%20giants%20might%20face%20more%20enforcement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKent%20Walker%2C%20Google's%20president%20of%20global%20affairs%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20company%20planned%20to%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20decision%20recognizes%20that%20Google%20offers%20the%20best%20search%20engine%2C%20but%20concludes%20that%20we%20shouldn't%20be%20allowed%20to%20make%20it%20easily%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20Walker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvelyn%20Mitchell-Wolf%2C%20a%20senior%20analyst%20at%20Emarketer%2C%20said%20that%20Google's%20loss%20%26quot%3Bcould%20be%20a%20huge%20deal%20%E2%80%94%20depending%20on%20the%20remedy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20could%20be%20forced%20to%20divest%20its%20search%20business%2C%20she%20said%2C%20or%20lose%20the%20ability%20to%20strike%20deals%20to%20be%20the%20exclusive%20search%20engine%20across%20various%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Mitchell-Wolf%20noted%20%26quot%3Ba%20drawn-out%20appeals%20process%20will%20delay%20any%20immediate%20effects%20for%20consumers%20%E2%80%94%20or%20advertisers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d55aaa9-a7b9-4d30-8eb8-1c5171fb5704%5C%22%3ELarger%20implications%20for%20Big%20Tech%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20first%20filed%20suit%20against%20Google%20in%202020%2C%20it%20alleged%20the%20company's%20deals%20to%20be%20the%20default%20search-engine%20provider%20on%20various%20devices%2C%20including%20iPhones%2C%20violated%20healthy%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20trial%2C%20it%20emerged%20that%20Google%20paid%20%2426%20billion%20in%202021%20to%20different%20smartphone%20makers%20%E2%80%94%20with%20Apple's%20cut%20being%20about%20%2418%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F05%2F02%2Ftechnology%2Fgoogle-antitrust-trial-closing-arguments.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20chief%20Satya%20Nadella%20and%20Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20testified%20during%20the%2010-week%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Google's%20legal%20battle%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20the%20most%20consequential%20antitrust%20case%20in%20Big%20Tech%20since%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-1990s-antitrust-case-looms-over-apple-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMicrosoft's%20battle%20in%20the%20late%20'90s%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20tech%20company%20not%20alone%20in%20facing%20regulatory%20blowback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DOJ%20filed%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-antitrust-lawsuit-justice-department-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eantitrust%20suit%20against%20Apple%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%2C%20accusing%20the%20iPhone%20maker%20of%20stifling%20competition%20in%20the%20smartphone%20market.%20And%20last%20September%2C%20the%20FTC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-used-secret-algorithm-raise-rival-site-prices-antitrust-lawsuit-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esued%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20inflating%20prices%20and%20overcharging%20smaller%20sellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20were%20looking%20to%20Mehta's%20ruling%20as%20a%20bellwether%20for%20how%20future%20cases%20could%20ultimately%20be%20resolved.%20Now%2C%20Big%20Tech%20has%20its%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-violated-antitrust-law-to-keep-search-monopoly-judge-rules-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722889745000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b121e2393cd3c8629b6047%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A