C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Clarence%20Thomas%20wearing%20his%20robes%20and%20looking%20down%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b12481a5247369a3e9913e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESen.%20Ron%20Wyden%20lists%2019%20trips%20that%20Thomas%20has%20taken%20on%20Crow's%20private%20jet%20since%202010.%3Cp%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EClarence%20Thomas%20didn't%20disclose%20a%202010%20trip%20on%20billionaire%20Harlan%20Crow's%20jet%2C%20a%20Democratic%20senator%20alleged.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20allegations%20are%20part%20of%20a%20Senate%20investigation%20into%20Crow's%20taxes%20and%20financial%20ties%20to%20Thomas.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20week%20ago%2C%20Biden%20proposed%20huge%20changes%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20including%20a%20binding%20code%20of%20conduct.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESupreme%20Court%20Justice%20Clarence%20Thomas%20missed%20publicly%20disclosing%20another%20jaunt%20on%20billionaire%20and%20conservative%20megadonor%20Harlan%20Crow's%20private%20jet%2C%20Democratic%20Sen.%20Ron%20Wyden%20of%20Oregon%20alleged%20in%20a%20letter%20on%20Monday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.finance.senate.gov%2Fimo%2Fmedia%2Fdoc%2Fchairman_wyden_to_harlan_crow_-_080524pdf.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Thomas%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Virginia%20Thomas%2C%20took%20a%20round-trip%20flight%20on%20Crow's%20private%20jet%20from%20Hawaii%20to%20New%20Zealand%20in%20November%20of%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWyden%2C%20who%20is%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Senate%20Finance%20Committee%2C%20sent%20the%20letter%20to%20Crow's%20lawyers%20as%20part%20of%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20ties%20between%20the%20right-wing%20donor%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20justice.%20In%20it%2C%20he%20writes%20that%20Customs%20and%20Border%20patrol%20records%20show%20evidence%20of%20the%20trip%2C%20but%20that%20Thomas%20did%20not%20list%20it%20on%20his%202010%20financial%20disclosures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustices%20are%20legally%20obligated%20to%20fill%20out%20financial%20disclosure%20forms%20every%20year%2C%20which%20include%20any%20external%20sources%20of%20income%20and%20gifts.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20had%20amended%20some%20of%20his%20disclosure%20documents%20to%20include%20travel%20on%20Crow's%20jet%20after%20ProPublica%20revealed%20the%20lavish%20gifts%20and%20vacations%20Thomas%20received.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Thomas%20made%20no%20such%20edits%20to%20his%202010%20disclosures%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F08%2F05%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fclarence-thomas-harlan-crow-private-jet.html%3Fsmid%3Dnytcore-ios-share%26amp%3BreferringSource%3DarticleShare%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20Thomas%20has%20said%20that%20he%20doesn't%20think%20he%20needs%20to%20disclose%20gifts%20from%20friends%20who%20don't%20have%20business%20before%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20his%20letter%2C%20Wyden%20requests%20a%20%26quot%3Bdetailed%20list%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclarence-thomas-accepted-free-yacht-trip-to-putins-hometown-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eall%20flights%20Justice%20Clarence%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20taken%20on%20any%20private%20jets%20under%20Mr.%20Crow's%20ownership%20or%20control.%26quot%3B%20Under%20that%2C%20he%20enumerates%2019%20known%20flights%20between%202010%20and%202022%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20newly%20discovered%20trip%20from%20Hawaii%20to%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20is%20part%20of%20a%20congressional%20investigation%20into%20whether%20Crow%20is%20improperly%20listing%20the%20gifts%20on%20his%20tax%20records.%20In%20a%20statement%2C%20Crow's%20lawyers%20said%20that%20the%20senator's%20allegations%20%26quot%3Bhave%20no%20legal%20basis%20and%20are%20only%20intended%20to%20harass%20a%20private%20citizen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Thomas%20does%20list%20travel%20from%20Crow%2C%20he%20calls%20them%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20hospitality.%26quot%3B%20The%20Senate%20committee%2C%20Wyden%20said%2C%20is%20seeking%20evidence%20that%20Crow%20has%20not%20listed%20the%20trips%20as%20business%20expenses%20and%20received%20tax%20deductions%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20Thomas%20nor%20Wyden%20immediately%20responded%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESupreme%20Court%20ethics%20have%20been%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20some%20time%2C%20and%20the%20new%20revelations%20come%20just%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-aims-rein-in-supreme-court-saying-its-gone-rogue-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Biden%20proposed%20sweeping%20changes%20at%20the%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20a%20binding%20code%20of%20conduct.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Biden's%20proposals%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-supreme-court-reform-plan-dead-on-arrival-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunlikely%20to%20get%20Republican%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20keep%20the%20spotlight%20on%20an%20increasingly%20unpopular%20high%20court%20and%20on%20Thomas%20in%20particular%2C%20whose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrips-justice-clarence-thomas-took-with-harlan-crow-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emany%20trips%20with%20Crow%3C%2Fa%3E%20sparked%20much%20of%20the%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclarence-thomas-disclose-harlan-crow-jet-trip-hawaii-senator-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722887536000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.in