will%20be%20delayed%20is%20calling%20into%20question%20whether%20the%20company%20can%20deliver%20on%20its%20promise%20to%20launch%20a%20new%20chip%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rollout%20of%20Nvidia's%20next-generation%20of%20AI%20chips%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ceo-jensen-huang-unveils-next-generation-ai-chip-blackwell-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlackwell%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20going%20to%20be%20delayed%20according%20to%20media%20and%20industry%20analyst%20reports.%20Though%20a%20few%20Blackwell%20chips%20are%20already%20in%20customers'%20hands%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company%2C%20the%20ramp-up%20to%20full-scale%20production%20was%20supposed%20to%20come%20this%20fall.%20It%20will%20now%20be%20delayed%20two%20to%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chip%20experts%20at%20research%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.semianalysis.com%2Fp%2Fnvidias-blackwell-reworked-shipment%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESemianalysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%20Sunday%20that%20Nvidia%20is%20facing%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20issues%20in%20reaching%20high%20production%20volume%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20Hopper%20chips%20would%20likely%20be%20sent%20to%20customers%20instead%20of%20the%20delayed%20Blackwell%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Information%20reported%20Friday%20that%20some%20Blackwell%20shipments%20would%20now%20be%20pushed%20to%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20next%20year%20when%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20had%20promised%20revenue%20from%20Blackwell%20by%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20largest%20customers%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-big-tech-earnings-week-early-winner-ai-microsoft-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Smaller%20cloud%20firms%20that%20have%20built%20their%20businesses%20on%20Nvidia%20chips%20could%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20delay%20too.%