o%20a%20developed%20country%20and%20she%20worked%20so%20hard%20for%20it%20over%20the%20last%2015%20years%2C%20keeping%20it%20safe%20from%20militants%20and%20as%20well%20as%20from%20terrorism%20and%20in%20spite%20of%20all%20of%20that%20this%20vocal%20minority%2C%20the%20opposition%2C%20the%20militants%20have%20now%20seized%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20flight%20came%20less%20than%20seven%20months%20after%20she%20celebrated%20a%20fourth%20straight%20term%20in%20power%20-%20and%20fifth%20overall%20-%20by%20sweeping%20national%20elections%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2076-year-old%20was%20flown%20in%20a%20military%20helicopter%20on%20Monday%20with%20her%20sister%20to%20take%20refuge%20in%20India.%20She%20is%20expected%20to%20leave%20for%20London%20later%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%2C%20where%20she%20may%20seek%20political%20asylum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20son%2C%20however%2C%20said%20he%20did%20not%20discuss%20with%20her%20where%20she%20is%20headed%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20last%2015%20years%20in%20power%20were%20marked%20by%20arrests%20of%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20crackdowns%20on%20free%20speech%20and%20suppression%20of%20dissent%2C%20and%20she%20resigned%20in%20the%20face%20of%20deadly%20student-led%20protests%20that%20have%20killed%20hundreds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtests%20began%20in%20June%20after%20student%20groups'%20demands%20for%20the%20scrapping%20of%20a%20controversial%20quota%20system%20in%20government%20jobs%20escalated%20into%20a%20movement%20seeking%20the%20end%20of%20her%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20that%20there%20will%20be%20elections%20in%20Bangladesh%20but%20at%20this%20time%20with%20our%20party%20leaders%20being%20targeted%20I%20don't%20see%20how%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20would%20be%20possible.%20In%20a%20way%2C%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20family's%20responsibility.%20We%20have%20shown%20what%20we%20can%20do.%20We%20have%20shown%20How%20much%20we%20can%20develop%20Ban