0camera%2C%20looting%20furniture%20and%20books%2C%20or%20relaxing%20on%20beds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20said%20it%20would%20lift%20a%20curfew%20imposed%20to%20quash%20protests%20at%20dawn%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20doubt%20army%20will%20be%20able%20to%20normalise%20things%20that%20fast.%20Because%20right%20now%20what%20is%20happening%20is%20that%20the%20opposition%20and%20the%20militants%2C%20they%20are%20not%20only%20vandalising%2C%20they%20are%20also%20hunting%20out%20our%20leaders%2C%20former%20ministers%20and%20even%20what%20I%20am%20hearing%20minorties.%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20violence%20has%20ended%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Joy.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMobs%20raided%20and%20ransacked%20the%20homes%20of%20Hasina's%20Awami%20League%20party%20allies%20as%20well%20as%20police%20stations%2C%20witnesses%20told%20news%20agency%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrowds%20smashed%20statues%20of%20her%20father%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman%2C%20the%20country's%20independence%20hero%2C%20and%20set%20fire%20to%20a%20museum%20dedicated%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20emotion%20is%20one%20of%20disappointment%2C%20anger%2C%20that%20my%20grandfather%20liberated%20the%20country%20and%20they%20killed%20him%20and%20my%20entire%20family.%20And%20now%20the%20same%20powers%2C%20these%20are%20the%20minorities%20that%20opposed%20the%20independence%20of%20Bangladesh%20are%20using%20this%20opportunity%20to%20basically%20deny%20and%20destroy%20our%20hard-fought%20struggle%20for%20freedom.%20And%20it's%20very%20disheartening%20to%20see%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20Bangladesh%20is%20staying%20silent%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Joy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20south%20Asian%20nation%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20coups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20declared%20an%20emergency%20in%20January%202007%20after%20widespread%20political%20unrest%20and%20installed%20a%20military-backed%20caretaker%20government%20for%20two%20years.%3Cbr%3E