-sen-and-vinay-pathak-was-a-masterclass-in-acting-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F112297258.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112297258.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESalim%20Diwan%2C%20who%20plays%20an%20abductor%20in%20'Aliya%20Basu%20Gayab%20Hai'%2C%20shares%20insights%20about%20his%20complex%20character%2C%20the%20challenges%20of%20making%20him%20relatable%2C%20and%20working%20with%20Raima%20Sen%20and%20Vinay%20Pathak.%20He%20discusses%20the%20film's%20psychological%20depth%2C%20his%20Hindi%20film%20industry%20journey%2C%20inspirations%2C%20and%20the%20profound%20impact%20of%20the%20Hajj%20tragedy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Milana%20Rao%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsalim-diwan-on-aliya-basu-gayab-hai-working-with-raima-sen-and-vinay-pathak-was-a-masterclass-in-acting-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F112297258.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Banker%20To%20Spiritual%20Guru%3A%20How%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Man%20Dodged%20CBI%20For%2020%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20swindler's%2020-year%20cat-and-mouse%20game%20with%20the%20law%20ended%20after%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20CBI%20while%20he%20was%20allegedly%20living%20as%20a%20spiritual%20guru%20in%20a%20Tamil%20Nadu%20village%20-%20one%20of%20the%20many%20aliases%20he%20used%20to%20dodge%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20evade%20the%20law%2C%20V%20Chalapathi%20Rao%20allegedly%20created%20multiple%20fake%20identities%2C%20forged%20new%20Aadhaar%20cards%2C%20lived%20in%20many%20states%20and%20took%20up%20jobs%20as%20a%20computer%20operator%20and%20a%20loan%20recovery%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao%20was%20arrested%20on%20Sunday%20from%20Narsinganallur%20village%20in%20Tirunelveli%20before%20he%20could%20flee%20yet%20again%2C%20this%20time%20to%20another%20country%2C%20officials%20said%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20had%20registered%20a%20case%20on%20May%201%2C%202002%20against%20Rao%2C%20who%20was%20then%20working%20as%20a%20computer%20operator%20in%20SBI%2C%20Chandulal%20Biradari%20branch%2C%20Hyderabad%20on%20allegations%20that%20he%20had%20siphoned%20off%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20from%20the%20bank%20using%20fabricated%20quotations%20of%20electronic%20shops%20and%20fake%20salary%20certificates%20created%20in%20the%20names%20of%20his%20family%20members%20and%20close%20associates%2C%20and%20misappropriated%20the%20proceeds%20of%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20chargesheets%20were%20filed%20in%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%2020%20years%2C%20his%20family%20made%20an%20attempt%20to%20declare%20him%20dead%2C%20seven%20years%20after%20he%20went%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20created%20an%20Aadhaar%20card%20in%20the%20name%20of%20one%20M%20Vineet%20Kumar%20and%20married%20again%20in%20Salem%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20(first)%20wife%2C%20who%20is%20also%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20above%20fraud%20case%2C%20even%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20at%20Kamatipura%20Police%20Station%20dated%20July%2010%2C%202004.%20She%20had%20also%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Civil%20Court%20to%20declare%20the%20absconding%20accused%20as%20dead%20after%20completion%20of%207%20years%20after%20PO%20allegedly%20went%20missing.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20an%20order%2Fdecree%20too%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20concerned%20Civil%20Court%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20CBI%20Spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20later%20declared%20a%20proclaimed%20offender%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao's%20second%20wife%20told%20the%20CBI%20that%20he%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20his%20son%20from%20his%20first%20wife%20but%20before%20the%20agency%20could%20reach%20him%2C%20he%20fled%20to%20Bhopal%20in%202014%20where%20worked%20as%20loan%20recovery%20agent%20and%20then%20shifted%20to%20Rudrapur%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20where%20he%20worked%20in%20a%20school%2C%20the%20CBI%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ensuing%20cat-and-mouse%20game%2C%20the%20CBI%20team%20tracked%20him%20to%20Rudrapur%20but%20returned%20empty%20handed%20as%20he%20had%20fled%20from%20Uttarakhand%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20then%20took%20help%20of%20Gmail's%20department%20that%20handles%20requests%20from%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20by%20providing%20it%20with%20Aadhaar%20card%20information%20of%20M%20Vineet%20Kumar%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20came%20to%20know%20Rao%20had%20shifted%20to%20an%20ashram%20in%20Verul%20village%2C%20Aurangabad%20but%20he%20had%20managed%20to%20get%20another%20Aadhaar%20card%20for%20a%20new%20alias%2C%20thus%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20identify%20him%20In%20Aurangabad%2C%20he%20was%20living%20as%20Swamy%20Vidhitatmanand%20Teertha.%20Even%20as%20a%20spiritual%20guru%2C%20Rao%20had%20allegedly%20cheated%20the%20ashram%20where%20he%20was%20staying%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%2070%20lakh%20before%20fleeing%20to%20Bharatpur%2C%20Rajasthan%20in%20December%202021%20where%20he%20continued%20to%20stay%20as%20an%20ascetic%20till%20July%208%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao%20allegedly%20kept%20changing%20phone%20numbers%2C%20around%208-10%20times%20during%20the%20period%2C%20and%20even%20had%20planned%20to%20escape%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20using%20the%20sea%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20he%20allegedly%20fled%20from%20Bharatpur%20and%20reached%20Narsinganallur%20village%20in%20Tirunelveli%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20stay%20with%20one%20of%20his%20disciples%20and%20keep%20working%20on%20his%20plan%20to%20move%20to%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20plans%20failed%20to%20take%20off%20as%20the%20CBI%20got%20information%20about%20his%20presence%20in%20the%20village%20where%20he%20was%20arreste