0stated%20that%20it%20has%20carefully%20considered%20the%20request%20of%20Puja%20Khedkar%20and%20in%20order%20to%20meet%20the%20ends%20of%20justice%2C%20she%20was%20granted%20time%20till%203%3A30%20pm%20of%2030th%20July%2C%202024%20so%20as%20to%20enable%20her%20to%20submit%20the%20response%20to%20the%20show%20cause%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20categorically%20made%20clear%20to%20Puja%20Khedkar%20that%20it%20was%20last%20and%20final%20opportunity%20to%20her%20and%20no%20further%20extension%20in%20time%20would%20be%20allowed.%20It%20was%20also%20conveyed%20to%20her%20in%20unequivocal%20terms%20that%20if%20no%20response%20was%20received%20by%20the%20aforesaid%20date%2Ftime%2C%20the%20UPSC%20would%20take%20further%20action%20without%20entertaining%20any%20further%20reference%20from%20her.%20Despite%20extension%20in%20time%20allowed%20to%20her%2C%20she%20failed%20to%20submit%20her%20explanation%20within%20the%20prescribed%20time%2C%20stated%20UPSC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UPSC%20has%20examined%20the%20available%20records%20carefully%20and%20found%20her%20guilty%20of%20acting%20in%20contravention%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20CSE-2022%20Rules.%20Her%20provisional%20candidature%20for%20the%20CSE-2022%20has%20been%20cancelled%20and%20she%20has%20also%20been%20debarred%20permanently%20from%20all%20the%20future%20Examinations%2FSelections%20of%20the%20UPSC%2C%20press%20statement%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%20Delhi%20Patiala%20House%20Court%20has%20dismissed%20the%20anticipatory%20bail%20plea%20of%20Puja%20Khedkar%2C%20and%20said%20the%20allegations%20against%20the%20accused%20Puja%20Khedkar%20are%20grave%20and%20serious%20which%20requires%20thorough%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCustodial%20interrogation%20of%20the%20accused%20is%20required%20to%20unearth%20the%20whole%20conspiracy%20and%20to%20establish%20involvement%20of%20the%20other%20persons%20involved%20in%20conspiracy.%20In%20the%20present%20facts%20and%20circumstances%2C%20I%20am%20of%20the%20considered%20opinion%20that%20it%20is%20not%20a%20fit%20case%20to%20exercise%20discretionary%20powers%20of%20anticipatory%20bail%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20said%20Additional%20Sessions%20Judge%20Devender%20Kumar%20Jangala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECourt%20noted%20that%20in%20the%20present%20case%20the%20applicant%2Faccused%20has%20been%20charged%20for%20Commission%20of%20offence%20punishable%20under%20Section%20420%2F468%2F471%2F120B%20IPC%20and%2066D%20IT%20Act%20and%2089%2F91%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disability%20Act%2C%202016.%20The%20applicant%2Faccused%20has%20cheated%20the%20complainant%20by%20mis%20representation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigating%20agency%20also%20needs%20to%20widen%20its%20scope%20of%20investigation.%20Hence%20the%20investigating%20agency%20is%20directed%20to%20conduct%20its%20investigation%20in%20all%20fairness%20to%20find%20out%20the%20candidates%20recommended%20in%20recent%20past%20(a)%20Who%20have%20illegally%20availed%20the%20attempts%20beyond%20permissible%20limits%3B%20(b)%20who%20have%20obtained%20the%20OBC(non%20creamy%20layer)%20benefit%2C%20despite%20not%20being%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Eentitled%3B%20(c)%20Who%20had%20obtained%20the%20benefits%20of%20persons%20with%20benchmark%20disability%2C%20despite%20being%20not%20entitled%20and%20(d)%20the%20investigating%20agency%20shall%20also%20find%20out%20whether%20some%20insider%20from%20the%20complainant%20side%20has%20also%20helped%20the%20applicant%20to%20attain%20her%20illegal%20goals%2C%20stated%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPuja%20Khedkar%20recently%20filed%20anticipatory%20bail%20application%20in%20relation%20to%20a%20FIR%20registered%20against%20her%20for%20allegedly%20%26quot%3Bfaking%20her%20identity%20to%20fraudulently%20avail%20attempts%20beyond%20permissible%20limit%26quot%3B%20in%20civil%20services%20examination.%20Recently%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20registered%20a%20FIR%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20complaint%20filed%20by%2