ged%20the%20complexion%20of%20the%20match%20as%20the%20world%20number%207%20Malaysian%20registered%20a%2013-21%2021-16%2021-11%20win%20in%20a%2071-minute%20clash%20to%20secure%20the%20bronze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20my%20chances%20in%20the%20second%20set%20and%20could%20have%20definitely%20done%20better.%20But%20credit%20to%20him%2C%20he%20played%20a%20really%20good%20game.%20I%20think%20at%20the%20moment%20I'm%20just%20not%20able%20to%20think%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20crestfallen%20Sen%20said%20after%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20came%20well%20prepared%20for%20this%20match%20as%20well.%20It%20has%20been%20quite%20a%20tough%20week%20overall.%20But%20yeah%2C%20the%20fatigue%20kept%20on%20building.%20But%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20give%20my%20100%20per%20cent%20in%20this%20match.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESen%2C%20who%20needed%20medical%20attention%20multiple%20times%20for%20a%20injured%20right%20arm%2C%20looked%20indomitable%20in%20the%20first%2030%20minutes%20but%20once%20Lee%20gathered%20himself%20from%20a%20position%20where%20he%20was%20down%20by%20a%20game%20and%20trailing%203-8%20in%20second%2C%20the%20Indian%20did%20not%20seem%20to%20have%20a%20plan%20'B'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESen%20need%20to%20replace%20his%20bandage%2C%20which%20was%20covered%20an%20injury%2C%20thrice%20during%20the%20match%2C%20leading%20to%20multiple%20stoppages%20in%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20said%20it%20affected%20his%20momentum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20between%20the%20points%20there%20was%20blood%20was%20on%20the%20floor%20so%20they%20had%20to%20wipe%20it.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20was%20losing%20the%20momentum%20of%20just%20having%20a%20break%20in%20the%20game%20and%20then%20coming%20again%20and%20trying%20to%20refocus%20on%20the%20match.%20But%20overall%20the%20hand%20is%20okay%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20loss%20means%20that%20it%20would%20be%20the%20first%20time%20in%2012%20years%20that%20India%20will%20return%20without%20a%20badminton%20medal%20from%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20Saina%20Nehwal%20(2012)%20and%20PV%20Sindhu%20(2016%2C%202021)%20have%20won%20Olympic%20medals%20for%20India%20at%20the%20biggest%20sporting%20stage%20with%20the%20latter's%20silver%20in%20Rio%20being%20the%20best%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20medal-favourite%20men's%20doubles%20pair%20of%20Satwaiksairaj%20Rankireddy%20and%20Chirag%20Shetty%20had%20also%20returned%20empty-handed%20as%20India's%20badminton%20campaign%20ended%20on%20a%20disappointing%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20member%20of%20the%20Indian%20badminton%20team%20and%20a%20part%20of%20the%20historic%20Thomas%20Cup%20winning%20squad%2C%20Sen%20was%20gunning%20to%20become%20India's%20first%20male%20shuttler%20to%20win%20an%20Olympic%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20match%20began%20with%20a%20long%20rally%20but%20Sen%20hit%20top%20gear%20early.%20The%20Indian%20largely%20played%20on%20the%20backhand%20side%20of%20his%20rival%2C%20logging%20easy%20points%20as%20there%20was%20no%20fight%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20calculated%20drop%20shots%20set%20up%20easy%20points%20for%20Sen%20as%20he%20drew%20his%20rival%20on%20the%20forecourt.%20Even%20the%20Malaysian%20tried%20to%20play%20on%20backhand%20of%20Sen%20but%20the%20India%20was%20hardly%20perturbed%2C%20leading%2011-6%20at%20the%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20sting%20or%20intent%20in%20Lee's%20shots%20as%20he%20just%20played%20very%20defensive%20and%20was%20catching%20up%20to%20erase%20the%20deficit%20which%20was%20increasing%20with%20each%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20smart%20play%20by%20the%20Malaysian%20was%20when%20he%20jumped%20for%20an%20overhead%20smash%20but%20dropped%20the%20shuttle%20forward%2C%20catching%20Sen%20wrong%20footed%20and%20then%20came%20up%20with%20a%20winner%20in%20open%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESen%20closed%20the%20first%20game%20when%20he%20hit%20a%20lightning%20fast%20backhand%20and%20Lee's%20return%20sailed%20over%20the%20baseline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20game%20also%20started%20on%20a%20similar%20note%20as%20in%20no%20time%2C%20Sen%20zoomed%20to%20a%208-3%20lead%20after%20peppering%20Lee%20on%20his%20backhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESen%20seemed%20to%20be%20pulling%20away%20but%20then%20there%20was%20a%20twist%20in%20the%20tale%20when%20he%20lost%20nine%20straight%20points%20allowing%20the%20Malaysian%20to%20fightback%20into%20the%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20returns%2C%20body%20smash%20and%20most%20importantly%20an%20intent%20from%20Lee%20who%20began%20moving%20the%20Indian%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%203-8%2C%20the%20Malaysian%20made%20it%2012-8%20and%20ran%20away%20with%20the%20game%2C%20forcing%20a%20decider.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELee%20made%20a%20powerful%20start%20to%20the%20game%20with%20ferocious%20smashes%20and%20continued%20with%20the%20strategy%20to%20run%20away%20with%20the%20game%20and%20match%20as%20Sen's%20attack%20completely%20fell%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20when%20Sen%20was%20in%20an%20advantageous%20position%20to%20kill%20the%20point%2C%20like%20at%202-7%2C%20he%20could%20not%20with%20Lee%20making%20incredible%20recovery%20and%20movement%20with%20his%20reflexes%20and%20powerful%20shots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20commanding%209-4%20lead%20and%20momentum%20on%20his%20side%2C%20Lee%20kept%20going%20hard%20at%20Sen%2C%20who%20was%20struggling%20to%20return%20the%20smashing%20returns.%20It%20ended%20in%20the%20same%20fashion%2C%20as%20Lee%20sent%20a%20body%20smash%20which%20the%20Indian%20could%20not%20return.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722872040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fvt99ahr_lakshya-sen_625x300_05_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fblood-on-the-floor-lakshya-sen-reveals-why-he-lost-momentum-to-finish-4th-in-paris-olym