d%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUncertainty%20has%20surrounded%20Bangladesh's%20ability%20to%20host%20the%202024%20ICC%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20from%20October%203-20%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20turmoil%20and%20subsequent%20resignation%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%2C%20who%20fled%20the%20country%20in%20an%20Air%20Force%20jet.%20With%20the%20tournament%20being%20less%20than%20two%20months%20away%20from%20starting%2C%20speculations%20have%20risen%20over%20the%20event%20being%20moved%20to%20an%20alternative%20venue%20if%20the%20unrest%20continues%20in%20Bangladesh.%20The%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20has%20stated%20nothing%20on%20this%20front%2C%20but%20have%20said%20they%20are%20closely%20monitoring%20developments%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20before%20deciding%20their%20next%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ICC%20is%20closely%20monitoring%20developments%20in%20coordination%20with%20the%20Bangladesh%20Cricket%20Board%20(BCB)%2C%20their%20security%20agencies%20and%20our%20own%20independent%20security%20consultants.%20Our%20priority%20is%20the%20safety%20and%20well-being%20of%20all%20participants%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20ICC%20spokesperson%20to%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20last%20month's%20ICC%20Annual%20Conference%20in%20Colombo%2C%20the%20matter%20of%20unrest%20in%20Bangladesh%20over%20a%20government%20jobs%20quota%20system%20was%20raised%20by%20a%20few%20member%20nations.%20But%20the%20issue%20was%20not%20on%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20four-day%20conference%20and%20hence%2C%20it%20wasn't%20discussed%20formally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETen%20teams%20will%20play%2023%20matches%20over%2018%20days%20of%202024%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20at%20two%20venues%20-%20Sher-e-Bangla%20National%20Cricket%20Stadium%20in%20Dhaka%20and%20the%20Sylhet%20International%20Cricket%20Stadium%20in%20Sylhet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20be%2010%20warm-up%20matches%20from%20September%2027%20to%20October%201%2C%20all%20taking%20place%20at%20BKSP%20in%20Dhaka.%20In%20May%2C%20the%20ICC%20announced%20the%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20schedule%20in%20Dhaka%2C%20where%20Hasina%20was%20present%20alongside%20India%20captain%20Harmanpreet%20Kaur%20and%20Bangladesh%20skipper%20Nigar%20Sultana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20are%20in%20Group%20A%20alongside%20New%20Zealand%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20defending%20champions%20Australia%2C%20while%20Group%20B%20comprises%20of%20hosts%20Bangladesh%2C%20England%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20West%20Indies%20and%20Scotland.%20Bangladesh%20are%20slated%20to%20host%20the%20tournament%20for%20the%20second%20time%20after%20last%20doing%20so%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2023%20World%20Cup%20runners%20up%20South%20Africa%20will%20play%20England%20in%20the%20opening%20match%20of%20the%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20It%20is%20followed%20by%20hosts%20Bangladesh%20facing%20Scotland%20in%20the%20evening%20match%20in%20Dhaka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%2C%20the%20defending%20champions%20and%20the%20most%20successful%20team%20in%20the%20event's%20history%2C%20will%20start%20their%20campaign%20on%20October%204%20in%20Sylhet%20against%20Sri%20Lanka.%20It%20is%20followed%20by%20India%20opening%20its%20campaign%20against%20New%20Zealand%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETop%20two%20teams%20from%20Group%20A%20and%20Group%20B%20will%20qualify%20for%20the%20semi-finals%2C%20scheduled%20for%20October%2017%20in%20Sylhet%2C%20and%20October%2018%20in%20Dhaka%20respectively.%20The%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20champions%20will%20be%20crowned%20in%20Dhaka%20on%20October%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722868620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fupokmhao_cas_625x300_05_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbangladesh-protests-hit-cricket-how-a-major-tournament-can-get-affected-6269661%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uncertainty%20has%20surrounded%20Bangladesh's%20ability%20to%20host%20the%20