20an%20exile%20after%20the%20assassination%20of%20her%20father%20by%20officers%20of%20the%20Bangladesh%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Mujibur%20Rehman%20--%20whose%20statue%20was%20vandalised%20in%20today's%20violence%20--%C2%A0%20was%20the%20charismatic%20leader%20who%20led%20East%20Pakistan%20to%20Independence%20and%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20new%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina%2C%20only%2028%20when%20Mujibur%20Rehman%20was%20assassinated%2C%20remained%20in%20exile%20from%201975%20to%20late%201980s.%20While%20in%20exile%2C%20she%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%20to%20head%20the%20party%20her%20father%20founded%20and%20on%20her%20return%2C%20dived%20into%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201996%2C%20she%20steered%20Awami%20League%20to%20victory%20in%20the%20national%20election%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20woman%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20years%20of%20her%20stewardship%20brought%20a%20phase%20of%20huge%20growth%20to%20Bangladesh%20in%20terms%20of%20both%20economy%20and%20infrastructure%20that%20led%20to%20rapid%20change%20in%20the%20living%20standards%20in%20what%20once%20was%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20poorest%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20strained%20relationship%20with%20the%20judiciary%20and%20handling%20of%20an%20earlier%20series%20of%20protests%20gave%20rise%20to%20a%20generation%20of%20critics%20who%20accused%20her%20of%20totalitarianism%20and%20autocracy.%20Her%20victory%20in%20two%20subsequent%20elections%20saw%20widespread%20allegations%20of%20rigging%20%E2%80%93%20adding%20layers%20of%20controversy%20to%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20most%20prominent%20leaders%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina's%20efforts%20to%20bring%20peace%20after%2025%20years%20of%20conflict%20in%20the%20Chittagong%20Hill%20Tracts%20was%20recognised%20by%20the%20UNESCO%20with%20the%20Houphouet-Boigny%20Peace%20Prize%20in%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20wave%20of%20student%20protests%20%E2%80%93%20which%20had%20started%20weeks%20ago%20as%20one%20about%20quota%20in%20government%20jobs%20to%20the%20families%20of%20freedom%20fighters%20%E2%80%93%20had%20unexpectedly%20snowballed%20into%20demands%20for%20her%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20violence%20continued%2C%20the%20army%20took%20action%20today%2C%20scripting%20what%20some%20see%20as%20the%20last%20chapter%20of%20the%20political%20career%20of%20the%20leader%20whose%20life%20has%20mirrored%20the%20ups%20and%20downs%20of%20the%20nation%20since%20her%20birth%20in%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20tumultuous%20career%2C%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20has%20faced%20grenade%20attacks%20and%20assassination%20attempts.%20She%20had%20been%20placed%20thrice%20under%20house%20arrest%20by%20the%20army%2C%20once%20over%20her%20opposition%20to%20the%20coup%20and%20assumption%20of%20power%20by.%20Lt.%20Gen.%20Hussain%20Muhammad%20Ershad.%20Many%20believe%20it%20is%20still%20too%20premature%20to%20compose%20her%20political%20epitaph.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722862260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fq3ftcvug_sheikh-hasina-_625x300_22_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffreedom-war-heros-daughter-to-villain-sheikh-hasinas-biggest-challenge-6269067%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sheikh%20Hasina%2C%2077%2C%20feted%20chief%20of%20the%20Awami%20League%20and%20three-time%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20stepped%20down%20today%20amid%20a%2045-minute%20ultimatum%20of%20the%20army%20and%20took%20a%20flight%20out%20of%20the%20violence-torn%20nation%20for%20an%20unknown%20destination.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffreedom-war-heros-daughter-to-villain-sheikh-hasinas-biggest-challenge-6269067%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffreedom-war-heros