%20the%20pandemic.%20Chandrashekhar%20went%20home%20during%20the%20first%20lockdown.%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20watch%20the%20news%20and%20read%20articles.%20Every%20day%2C%20I%20would%20see%20lakhs%20of%20workers%20struggling%20to%20get%20back%20to%20their%20hometowns%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWatching%20this%20might%20have%20been%20very%20tough%20for%20many%2C%20but%20it%20was%20a%20lived%20reality%20for%20millions%20like%20Sumit%20Kumar%2C%20a%20construction%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20Gopalganj%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Sumit%20had%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20for%20work.%20He%20walked%20for%20two%20days%20before%20hitching%20rides%20on%20buses%20and%20trucks%20to%20reach%20home%2C%20he%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20one%20week%20it%20took%20to%20reach%20home%20was%20the%20worst%20week%20of%20my%20life.%20There%20was%20nobody%20willing%20to%20help%20me%20in%20the%20area%20where%20I%20lived.%20I%20survived%20thanks%20to%20the%20benevolence%20of%20kind%20strangers%20and%20other%20workers%20like%20me.%20I%20vowed%20never%20to%20go%20back%20to%20Mumbai%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESumit%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20one%20who%20wished%20to%20work%20near%20his%20hometown.%20The%20nightmarish%20experience%20during%20the%20lockdown%20made%20many%20workers%20desire%20the%20same%2C%20but%20where%20were%20the%20jobs%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20country%20started%20opening%20up%20slowly%2C%20people%20had%20to%20maintain%20a%20six-foot%20distance%20in%20public%20places.%20How%20could%20100%20workers%20in%20a%20small%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowk%3C%2Fem%3E%20maintain%20distance%3F%20To%20understand%20their%20problems%20in%20detail%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20spent%20over%20four%20months%20assessing%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowks%3C%2Fem%3E%20across%20Bihar%2C%20Noida%2C%20and%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20construction%20sector%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20second-largest%20employer%20after%20agriculture.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Knight%20Frank%20%26amp%3B%20RICS%2C%2071%20million%20workers%20are%20estimated%20to%20be%20employed%20in%20this%20sector%20as%20of%202023%2C%20out%20of%20which%20over%2080%20percent%20are%20unskilled.%20When%20Chandrashekhar%20came%20across%20this%20statistic%2C%20he%20knew%20that%20there%20was%20a%20major%20gap%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20filled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20helps%20daily%20wage%20workers%20find%20jobs%20online%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359731%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDigital%20Labour%20Chowk%20helps%20daily%20wage%20workers%20find%20jobs%20online.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20are%20platforms%20for%20finding%20white-collar%20jobs%20like%20Linkedin%2C%20Naukri%2C%20Indeed%2C%20and%20more%2C%20why%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20there%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333562%2Fassam-daily-wager-diganta-das-launches-paratha-startup-inspiring-entrepreneur-in-food-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20for%20blue-collar%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20I%20decided%20to%20build%20one%20and%20move%20the%20physical%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowks%3C%2Fem%3E%20digital.%20Daily%20wage%20workers%20too%20should%20be%20able%20to%20look%20for%20jobs%20from%20the%20comfort%20of%20their%20homes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConvinced%20about%20his%20idea%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20job%20in%20September%202020%20with%20Rs%2020%2C000%20in%20his%20pocket.%20Having%20already%20quit%20CA%20preparation%20after%20finishing%20the%20Inter%20exams%2C%20his%20family%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20very%20happy.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20runs%20a%20small%20shop%20and%20sent%20me%20to%20Delhi%20for%20schooling.%20He%20wanted%20me%20to%20study%20well%20and%20find%20a%20good%20job.%20When%20I%20quit%20and%20returned%20home%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20explaining%20that%20I%20had%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20chuckles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20few%20months%20were%20difficult%20as%20he%20remembers%20%E2%80%9Clooking%20at%20the%20fan%E2%80%9D%20and%20surviving%20on%20the%20savings%20he%20had!%20Chandrashekhar%20then%20started%20looking%20for%20government%20schemes%20and%20loans%20that%20he%20could%20apply%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20registering%20%E2%80%98Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20Private%20Limited%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20found%20his%20first%20investor%20in%20an%20incubator%20in%20Pune.%20The%20startup%20received%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20August%202021%2C%20kicking%20off%20a%20series%20of%20grants%20and%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20building%20the%20website%20and%20application%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20legal%20and%20technical%20aspects%2C%20the%20founder%20had%20a%20big%20task%20in%20hand%3A%20getting%20customers%20and%20workers%20to%20sign%20up.%20After%20hiring%20seven%20members%20for%20his%20team%2C%20the%20next%20challenge%20was%20wooing%20the%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20for%20blue-collar%20workers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20most%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowks%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20a%20mobile%20shop%20or%20small%20grocery%20store%20nearby%2C%20Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20signed%20up%20these%20shop%20owners%20as%20business%20associates.%20They%20would%20help%20workers%20register%20on%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9EWHhrCBDV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9EWHhrCBDV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9EWHhrCBDV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20%23%F0%9D%9F%8F%20%F0%9D%90%82%F0%9D%90%A8%F0%9D%90%A7%F0%9D%90%AC%F0%9D%90%AD%F0%9D%90%AB%F0%9D%90%AE%F0%9D%90%9C%F0%9D%90%AD%F0%9D%90%A2%F0%9D%90%A8%F0%9D%90%A7%20%F0%9D%90%82%F0%9D%90%A8%F0%9D%90%A6%F0%9D%90%A9%F0%9D%90%9A%F0%9D%90%A7%F0%9D%90%B2%20%7C%20%F0%9D%90%83%F0%9D%90%A2%F0%9D%90%A0%F0%9D%90%A2%F0%9D%90%AD%F0%9D%90%9A%F0%9D%90%A5%20%F0%9D%90%8B%F0%9D%90%9A%F0%9D%90%9B%F0%9D%90%A8%F0%9D%90%AE%F0%9D%90%AB%20%F0%9D%90%82%F0%9D%90%A1%F0%9D%90%A8%F0%9D%90%B0%F0%9D%90%A4%20(%40digitallabourchowk)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%20months%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20and%20his%20team%20campaigned%20in%20these%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowks%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%2020-litre%20thermos%20jars%20filled%20with%20cold%20drinks%20like%20Roohafza.%20If%20it%20was%20winter%2C%20the%20drink%20was%2C%20of%20course%2C%20%3Cem%3Echai%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20spoke%20to%20them%20and%20explained%20what%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20do.%20This%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341766%2Fodisha-daily-wage-labourer-isak-munda-becomes-youtube-star-with-food-videos-watch%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20opportunity%20to%20escape%20a%20life%20of%20uncertainty%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20most%20migrant%20workers%20are%20from%20Bihar%2C%20we%20explained%20that%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20migrate%20all%20the%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Chandrashekhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20set%20up%20kiosks%20in%20highly%20populated%20districts%20to%20spread%20the%20word.%20To%20get%20contractors%2C%20project%20managers%20and%20companies%20on%20board%2C%20they%20partnered%20with%20builders%E2%80%99%20associations%20and%20Real%20Estate%20Regulatory%20Authority%20(RERA)%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Noida.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20joined%20over%20100%20construction%20groups%20on%20Facebook%20to%20build%20contacts%20and%20find%20customers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20is%20built%20for%20construction%20companies%20and%20workers%2C%20masons%2C%20painters%2C%20carpenters%2C%20etc.%20When%20a%20customer%20(contractor)%20signs%20up%2C%20they%20add%20details%20like%20location%2C%20kind%20of%20job%2C%20wages%20per%20day%2C%20number%20of%20days%20for%20which%20labour%20is%20required%2C%20and%20whether%20accommodation%20and%20food%20are%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorkers%20can%20access%20these%20details%20and%20call%20the%20job%20poster%20directly%20to%20express%20their%20interest.%20On%20the%20workers%E2%80%99%20side%2C%20they%20add%20details%20like%20their%20skills%2C%20past%20experiences%2C%20and%20minimum%20wages.%20Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20is%20working%20to%20make%20digital%20labour%20cards%20for%20these%20workers%2C%20which%20will%20provide%20them%20with%20an%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20also%20planning%20to%20give%20incentives%20based%20on%20their%20performance%20to%20boost%20their%20morale.%20This%20is%20our%20effort%20to%20organise%20the%20informal%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20Noida%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECustomers%20get%2010%20connections%20for%20free%2C%20post%20which%20they%20pay%20a%20subscription%20fee.%20Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20is%20free%20for%20workers.%20The%20company%20is%20also%20in%20the%20process%20of%20partnering%20with%20institutes%20to%20provide%20upskilling%20courses%20for%20the%20workers%2C%20as%20there%20is%20a%20dearth%20of%20skilled%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShrawan%20Kumar%20from%20Darbhanga%20has%20been%20free%20of%20worry%20for%20the%20past%20year.%20He%20was%20employed%20by%20a%20builder%20in%20Jodhpur%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20on%20a%20long-term%20contract.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20earned%20in%20one%20year%20what%20I%20used%20to%20earn%20in%20three%20years.%20We%20also%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20stand%20in%20the%20heat%20daily%20looking%20for%20jobs.%20When%20one%20contract%20is%20about%20to%20end%2C%20we%20can%20choose%20the%20next%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20projects%20last%20for%20at%20least%2021%20days%2C%20according%20to%20Chandrashekhar.%20He%20claims%20that%20there%20are%20500%20to%201%2C000%20jobs%20posted%20daily%20on%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzhar%20Ansari%2C%20who%20runs%20an%20Uttar%20Pradesh-based%20construction%20company%2C%20explains%20that%20they%20are%20always%20short%20of%20manpower.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20hire%20workers%20as%20we%20fall%20short.%20We%20just%20put%20in%20our%20criteria%20on%20the%20app%20and%20we%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20workers%20according%20to%20the%20requirements%20from%20Digital%20Labour%20Chowk.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20good%20effort%20and%20makes%20the%20hiring%20process%20easy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognised%20by%20Startup%20Bihar%2C%20Startup%20India%2C%20Citibank%2C%20and%20more%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20is%20rearing%20to%20go.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20provide%20a%20credible%20virtual%20identity%20for%20these%20workers.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20transform%20this%20unorganised%2C%20unidentified%20sector%2C%20and%20provide%20them%20visibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESumit%20Kumar%20agrees%2C%20as%20he%20no%20longer%20has%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20his%20family%20for%20months%2C%20now%20that%20he%20can%20find%20options%20nearby!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3B%20Images%20Courtesy%20Chandrashekar%20Mandal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722845966000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk1-1722844675.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359592%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chandrashekhar%20Mandal%20started%20Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20to%20support%20daily%20wage%20labourers%20by%20connecting%20them%20with%20employers%20through%20an%20online%20platform.%20Inspired%20by%20the%20struggles%20of%20blue-collar%20workers%20in%20his%20family%20and%20hometown%2C%20he%20aims%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20dignity%2C%20identity%2C%20and%20a%20steady%20income.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukrainian%20a