ike%20shouting%20and%20rocking%20himself%2C%20for%20Navneet%20it%20means%20moving%20his%20fingers%20up%20and%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20my%20behaviour%20may%20look%20funny%20to%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20provides%20him%20recourse%20when%20he%20is%20in%20a%20high-activity%20zone.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20go%20out%2C%20all%20the%20surroundings%20distract%20my%20vision%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20my%20body%20is%20flying%20and%20my%20head%20is%20banging.%20To%20balance%20my%20sensory%20system%20I%20do%20stimming.%20I%20feel%20safe%20and%20comfortable%20when%20I%20fidget%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20treat%20us%20like%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20exist%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Chitra%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Tarun%20Paul%20Mathew%20(17)%2C%20the%20saddest%20reality%20is%20losing%20one%E2%80%99s%20identity.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20true%20for%20many%20of%20us%20non-speaking%20autistics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%20But%20writing%2C%20he%20says%2C%20has%20helped%20position%20him%20and%20other%20neurodivergent%20individuals%20(who%20are%20unable%20to%20communicate%20through%20speech)%20on%20the%20same%20level%20playing%20field%20as%20their%20neurotypical%20counterparts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-02-at-6.19.32-PM_11zon-1721808799-500x750.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chitra%20Paul%2C%20co-editor%20of%20Talking%20Fingers%2C%20with%20her%20son%20Tarun%20Paul%20Mathew%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-02-at-6.19.32-PM_11zon-1721808799-500x750.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fu