%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Ranjita%20Phukan%20Gogoi%20(%40ranjitaphukangogoi)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20couple%20was%20often%20invited%20to%20pool%20parties.%20While%20everyone%20swam%20around%20and%20had%20a%20gala%20time%2C%20including%20Mr%20Gogoi%2C%20the%20Mrs%20had%20to%20use%20a%20float.%20This%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20burning%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332716%2Fjanaki-amma-swimming-lessons-for-women-kids-reduce-drowning-deaths-in-kerala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesire%20to%20learn%20swimming%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20almost%20like%20an%20inferiority%20complex.%20While%20everyone%20enjoyed%20themselves%2C%20I%20was%20stuck%20in%20the%20sidelines.%20Couples%20swam%20together%20while%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20join%20my%20husband%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ranjita%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20in%20the%20early%2090s%20and%20after%20they%20returned%20to%20India%2C%20the%20swimming%20dream%20remained%20unfulfilled%20as%20there%20was%20no%20swimming%20pool%20nearby.%20By%20the%20time%2C%20their%20family%20too%20had%20grown%20and%20Ranjita%20juggled%20motherhood%20with%20her%20job.%20However%2C%20she%20had%20to%20quit%20in%20a%20few%20years%2C%20a%20regret%20which%20haunts%20Anjumon%20till%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20in%20nursery%20school%20and%20would%20miss%20my%20mom%20after%20coming%20back%20home.%20I%20would%20cry%20and%20tell%20her%20to%20be%20at%20home%20due%20to%20which%20she%20quit%20her%20job%20and%20never%20joined%20back.%20I%20regret%20it%20even%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjita%20kept%20herself%20busy%20tending%20to%20her%20beautiful%20garden%2C%20a%20hobby%20that%20she%20continues%20even%20today%20amidst%20her%20hectic%20schedule.%20She%20was%20soon%20kept%20busie